# Project Context

**At the start of every conversation, before taking any action**, read `/DECISIONS.md` in full. This file contains architectural decisions, conventions, and constraints that govern all work in this project. Do not rely on memory or assumptions — always read the file fresh.

When significant decisions are made during a conversation, update DECISIONS.md to reflect them before the conversation ends.
